title: Detail Template Test Demo
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Demonstrates the ''detail-template'' attribute, which controls how expanded tiddler content is rendered.  The template below adds a linked title above each entry's body.

<$simple-outline class="outline" detail-template="$:/_/so/templates/detail-test" text="""
!! Theoretical Foundations

  Mathematical Precursors
    + note-boole-algebra
    + note-babbage-engine

  Computability Theory
    + note-turing-machines
    + note-church-lambda
"""/>
